videos.headline: Dameon Pierce crosses the plane for Florida's first TD
videos.description: Dameon Pierce gets pushed back at the goal line, but his persistence pays off the second time as Florida takes the lead over UCF.

videos.headline: Isaiah Bowser scores for UCF with 3-yard TD run
videos.description: UCF's Isaiah Bowser runs it into the end zone for his eighth touchdown of the season

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (End Zone! Isaiah Bowser scores 3-yard rushing TD) 2021/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's O-line pushes Bowser into the end zone for second TD
videos.description: Isaiah Bowser scores his second touchdown of the game as UCF retakes the lead over Florida.

videos.headline: Malik Davis breaks through the heart of UCF's defense for the TD
videos.description: Florida takes the lead back after Malik Davis' 19-yard run through the middle of UCF's defensive line.

videos.headline: Ryan O'Keefe loses his defender and hauls in 54-yard TD for UCF

videos.headline: UCF gets first-ever win vs. Florida in Gasparilla Bowl
videos.description: The Knights beat Florida 29-17 to finish 9-4 in Gus Malzahn's first season as head coach.
